<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nunito" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;">
    <center>
        <table align="center" style="max-width: 717px; border-spacing: 0px;">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0 0 0;">
                        <img src="https://vdoctor-dev.s3.amazonaws.com/utils/logo_full.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin: 30px 0 10px;">
                        <img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/image-professional-woman-doctor-physician-with-clipboard-writing-listening-patient-hospital-cl_1258-122379.jpg?size=626&ext=jpg&ga=GA1.2.1038770876.1657780276&semt=ais"
                            width="100%" alt="">
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <div
                        style="background-color: #fff; border: 1px solid #f1f1f1; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 6px 24px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08) 0px 0px 0px 1px;">
                        <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #3F68F4; font-size: 29px; font-weight: 500;">Payment Confirmation
                        </h1>
                        <h4 style="font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px;">Hello <span style="font-weight: 700;">
                                <%= patient_name%>
                            </span>
                        </h4>
                        <p>We hope this email finds you well. We are writing to confirm the receipt of your recent
                            payment for the appointment id <%= unique_id%>
                        </p>
                        <p>We would like to express our sincere appreciation for your prompt payment. Your cooperation
                            and timely
                            settlement of invoices/orders are integral to maintaining smooth operations and providing
                            you with the
                            best service possible.
                        </p>
                        <p>Below are the details of your payment:

                        </p>
                        <div
                            style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 42rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem; padding: 0 0;">
                            <div style="display: grid; gap: 0.375rem;">
                                <h1
                                    style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-block-start: 0.5em; margin-block-end: 0.5em;">
                                    Appointment Id #<%= unique_id%>
                                </h1>
                            </div>
                            <div style="display: grid; gap: 0.375rem;">
                                <h1
                                    style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-block-start: 0.5em; margin-block-end: 0.5em;">
                                    Payment successful</h1>
                                <div style="font-weight: 400; color: #6b7280;">Your payment was successfully processed.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div style="display: grid; gap: 0.375rem;">
                                <h1
                                    style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-block-start: 0.5em; margin-block-end: 0.5em;">
                                    Payment details</h1>
                                <div style="display: grid; gap: 0.375rem;">
                                    <div>Amount</div>
                                    <div style="font-weight: 600;">$<%= amount%>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div style="display: grid; gap: 0.375rem;" data-orientation="horizontal" role="none"
                                class="shrink-0 bg-gray-100"
                                style="height: 1px; width: 100%; border-top-width: 1px; border-color: #e2e8f0;"></div>
                            <div style="display: grid; gap: 0.375rem;">
                                <h1
                                    style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-block-start: 0.5em; margin-block-end: 0.5em;">
                                    Thank you for your payment!</h1>
                                <div style="font-weight: 400; color: #6b7280;">Your appointment is confirmed.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: end; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </center>
</body>

</html>